1. Večeras *noći* će biti hladne. (Tonight the *nights* will be cold.)
2. Prošle *noći* nisam mogao da zaspim. (Last *night* I couldn't fall asleep.)
3. Šetali smo *noću* i divili se gradu. (We walked at *night* and admired the city.)
4. *Noću* često čujem zvukove iz komšiluka. (I often hear sounds from the neighbors at *night*.)
5. Tokom *noći* se temperatura spustila ispod nule. (During the *night* the temperature dropped below zero.)
6. *Noćima* se čuje vrisak iz obližnje šume. (Screaming can be heard from the nearby forest at *night*.)
7. Još uvek je *noć* i nije vreme za ustajanje. (It's still *night* and it's not time to get up yet.)
8. Svetla u gradu se gase tokom *noći*. (The lights in the city go off during the *night*.)
9. Rekao sam joj da mi pošalje poruku kad stigne *noć*. (I told her to send me a message when *night* falls.)
10. Životinje su aktivnije *noću* nego danju. (Animals are more active at *night* than during the day.)